Class EncryptionInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.poifs.crypt.EncryptionInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericRecord 

    public class EncryptionInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements GenericRecord
    Wrapper for the EncryptionInfo node of encrypted documents(加密文档的EncryptionInfo节点的包装器)

      • ENCRYPTION_INFO_ENTRY

        public static final java.lang.String ENCRYPTION_INFO_ENTRY
        Document entry name for encryption info xml descriptor(加密信息html描述符的文档条目名称)
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • flagCryptoAPI

        public static final BitField flagCryptoAPI
        A flag that specifies whether CryptoAPI RC4 or ECMA-376 encryption ECMA-376 is used. It MUST be 1 unless flagExternal is 1. If flagExternal is 1, it MUST be 0.(指定是否使用CryptoAPI RC 4或ECMA-376加密ECMA-376的标志。除非flagExternal为1，否则它必须为1。如果flagExternal为1，则必须为0。)

      • flagDocProps

        public static final BitField flagDocProps
        A value that MUST be 0 if document properties are encrypted. The encryption of document properties is specified in section 2.3.5.4.(如果文档属性已加密，则该值必须为0。文档属性的加密在第2.3.5.4节中指定。)

      • flagExternal

        public static final BitField flagExternal
        A value that MUST be 1 if extensible encryption is used. If this value is 1, the value of every other field in this structure MUST be 0.(如果使用可扩展加密，则必须为1的值。如果此值为1，则此结构中每个其他字段的值必须为0。)

      • flagAES

        public static final BitField flagAES
        A value that MUST be 1 if the protected content is an ECMA-376 document ECMA-376. If the fAES bit is 1, the fCryptoAPI bit MUST also be 1.(如果受保护的内容是ECMA-376文档ECMA-376，则该值必须为1。如果fAES位为1，则fCryptoAPI位也必须为1。)

      • EncryptionInfo

        public EncryptionInfo(EncryptionMode encryptionMode,
                      CipherAlgorithm cipherAlgorithm,
                      HashAlgorithm hashAlgorithm,
                      int keyBits,
                      int blockSize,
                      ChainingMode chainingMode)
        Constructs an EncryptionInfo from scratch(从头开始构建加密信息)
        Parameters:
        encryptionMode - see EncryptionMode for values, EncryptionMode.cryptoAPI is for internal use only, as it's record based(CompettionMode-请参阅CryptionMode以获取值，CryptionMode。CryptoAPI仅供内部使用，因为它基于记录)
        cipherAlgorithm - the cipher algorithm(密码算法-密码算法)
        hashAlgorithm - the hash algorithm(哈希算法-哈希算法)
        keyBits - the bit count of the key(keyBits -键的位数)
        blockSize - the size of a cipher block(blockSize -密码块的大小)
        chainingMode - the chaining mode(chainingMode -链接模式)
        Throws:
        EncryptedDocumentException - if the given parameters mismatch, e.g. only certain combinations of keyBits, blockSize are allowed for a given CipherAlgorithm(CryptedDocument异常-如果给定参数不匹配，例如，给定的CipherAlgorithm仅允许keyBits、blockSize的某些组合)
